{"title":"Ritchey Butano Bar Integrates 1-piece SuperLogic Butano Ridge Carbon Cockpit","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ritchey-superlogic-butano-ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-cockpit/","date":1713957860000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_rider-view-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit\" /></p>\n<p>This new 1-piece carbon Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge adventure bar is a great example of combining the extremes of what Ritchey does best. Rider-focused ergonomics that open up more terrain for adventure riding. And sleek high-performance cockpit components that would make a solid upgrade for almost any bike…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge 1-piece carbon gravel bar</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike-1536x922.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, shouldered adventure gravel bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_on-bike.jpg 1800w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Ritchey)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We first saw the gently curving, compact Ritchey Butano adventure bar <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ritchey-twists-new-mtb-drop-bars-aero-stem-break-away-refresh-more/\" target=\"_blank\">five years ago in Taipei</a> when it debuted in affordable aluminum. In those years since, fully integrated cable routing has taken over, and both all-road and gravel bars have embraced more flared bar shapes. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top-1536x768.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, top view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top-297x149.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top-120x60.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top-768x384.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_top.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This new fast gravel SuperLogic Butano Ridge bar combines the best of both worlds. It’s a lightweight 1-piece monocoque carbon handlebar + stem combo with fully integrated cable routing channels, plus off-road ready flare and backsweep.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view-1536x864.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, front view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_front-view.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Butano means an ergonomic gravel shape. So the Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge gets 17.5° of flare to its drops from the hoods (<em>looking from the front</em>), plus a bit more with an extra 2° of flare just at the flat ends of the drops (<em>viewed from above</em>). And to tuck your elbows in, 5° of backsweep to the flattened rounded aero tops. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend-1536x1152.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, compact bend round drop\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_round-curve-compact-bend.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s Ritchey’s classic compact round bend, so 73mm of Reach and 115mm of Drop.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new bar+stem cockpit comes in two widths 42cm or 44cm, measured center-to-center at the hoods – which with the flare comes out 9.1cm wider at the ends of the drops. Effective stem lengths are 90, 100, or 110mm, with a -10° stem angle.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_underside-internal-routing-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1350\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_underside-internal-routing-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, underside internal routing detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_underside-internal-routing-detail.jpg 1350w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_underside-internal-routing-detail-297x158.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_underside-internal-routing-detail-120x64.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_underside-internal-routing-detail-768x410.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Cable routing is internal in the top of the bar, but never actually goes inside the stem. That way then, cables are relatively easy to manage and can be used with a variety of setups. Fully-internal, semi-internal, and conventional external routing setups. Cables exit the bar into a recessed channel under the stem. And one of two covers can direct them where needed. An integrated steerer spacer also can guide them into your headset. Like the internal routing <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ritchey-internal-routing-stems-corralitos-gravel-handlebar/\" target=\"_blank\">Ritchey Switch system</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, the same two bolts that secure these covers, serve as mounting points for a direct-mount out-front GPS mount.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, geometry drawings\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_geometry-768x461.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 1-piece Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge cockpit has a claimed weight of 417g for the largest 44cm x 110mm option. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge – Pricing, availability &amp; options</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio-1536x864.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, anglde\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_angled-studio.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new matte UD carbon Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge cockpit sells for $600 / 600€. You can get it in four sizes – 42cm/90mm, 42cm/100mm, 44cm/100mm, or 44cm/110mm. All feature a -10° stem and bar top designed for comfort at a variety of modern gravel bike head angles. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-1536x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Ritchey SuperLogic Butano Ridge fully-integrated 1-piece UD carbon gravel bar cockpit, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Ritchey-SuperLogic-Butano-Ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-stem-handlebar-cockpit_riding.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed for gravel racing, it can also bring some all-day ergonomic comfort and all-road control to your gravel bikes too. Get it now straight from Ritchey, or through your local bike shop.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RitcheyLogic.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ritchey-superlogic-butano-ridge-1-piece-integrated-carbon-gravel-bar-cockpit/\">Ritchey Butano Bar Integrates 1-piece SuperLogic Butano Ridge Carbon Cockpit</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9b358822c0f4d9ad8edffd0bf36a5bc906ef60cb06878e7da6883de496b246a4","category":"Cycling"}